node.text:
Custom 14k yellow gold skateboard charm. 🛹 

Show the world your passions with a custom charm. We are open for custom orders and can make your custom piece with yellow, white, rose, or champagne gold in any karat. Visit our custom page on our website to start your inquiry.

node.text:
I often get asked what inspires my designs, here is my attempt to answer that question. 
Also did you know that this is #nonbinaryweek and I am super happy to be here and be visible. It took me 29 years to come out as enby, and while I wish I realized it sooner, I am glad to finally be my true self!
